<a name="meet-studio-fovero"></a> 		<div id="top10">
			<div class="sub-content">

<div id="reasonsWrapper">
	<ul id="slider-reasons">

<li><img src="assets/images/staff/annie.png" alt="" />
<h4><div id="tvemployee-1">Annie</div></h4>
<div id="tvemployee-1-bio"><p>Annie just loves love. Go ahead and ask her... she\'ll tell you. She has been working her magic here at Fovero for almost 5 years. She is married to the love of her life and has 2 beautiful children. Her passion is (but certainly not limited to) styling hair. Whether it\'s for a wedding party or a fashion show, Annie knows how to make your hair look trendy, classy, or just plain beautiful. Girl knows how to braid, too! After a brief move to Boston and training in one of the trendiest salons in Downtown Boston she moved back to Ohio (and our Fovero family got our Annie back).</p></div>
</li>

<li><img src="assets/images/staff/amber.png" alt="" />
<h4><div id="tvemployee-2">Amber</div></h4>
<div id="tvemployee-2-bio"><p>Amber\'s love of beauty started young and officially her career in hair started in 2005 in Nashville, TN where she trained in a salon that specialized in corrective color. After moving to Columbus she knew she discovered her new home at Studio Fovero. Combining her passion for people and her creativity she seeks to enhance peoples\' natural beauty so their inner beauty shines through! She likes to leave every person with a customized look that is easy to maintain on their own. Amber is constantly seeking to grow as a stylist through continuing her education. With a great blowout and her bubbly personality (which has earned her the nickname Moonbeam) she will ensure you leave happy!</p></div>
</li>

<li><img src="assets/images/staff/brandon.png" alt="" />
<h4><div id="tvemployee-3">Brandon</div></h4>
<div id="tvemployee-3-bio"><p>This is Brandon... Studio Fovero\'s resident storyteller and bridal guru. He says his Momma raised a "gentleman" and he has a heart made of gold. Brandon started with us in 2008 and we\'re thinking we might definitely keep him around... just cause he\'s worth it (and so dang funny). He is extremely confident in all aspects of his craft and is about as dependable as they come. You are for sure to leave the salon with a smile on your face and some really great hair (he\'s also a hugger so you might get one of those too)!</p></div>
</li>

<li><img src="assets/images/staff/Ciarra.png" alt="" />
<h4><div id="tvemployee-4">Ciarra</div></h4>
<div id="tvemployee-4-bio"><p class="p1">This is Ciarra. She joined the Fovero team a couple of years ago and has totally made us all love her!!! Her youth is refreshing, her work ethic is out of this world, and her talent is limitless. Her passion for doing beautiful hair is exactly what everyone should look for in a hair stylist. She is very skilled in the art of balyage color and takes pride in not compromising the health of her clients\' hair. In addition to being passionate about hair, she is also super passionate about music and traveling and believe it or not her personality way outshines her beauty!!!</p></div>
</li>

<li><img src="assets/images/staff/katie.png" alt="" />
<h4><div id="tvemployee-5">Katie</div></h4>
<div id="tvemployee-5-bio"><p>Since Katie was a young lass she knew she was going to be some sort of a craftsman, working with her hands. She is a professional with a bright and vibrant personality, a dedicated work ethic, and devotion to client satisfaction. She is deeply invested in her clients and insists on having very thorough consultations to ensure that both parties feel 100% comfortable moving forward. She absolutely loves cutting and coloring, not one more than the other. Word on the street is that her shampoos are the bees knees.She is happily married to her best friend. She is also a daughter, sister, and awesome dog mom! When not at work, you will find Katie around a bonfire with family, friends, dogs, or on the stage singing backup vocals for Nick Tolford and Company! She’s also known to crack a few smiles!</p></div>
</li>

<li><img src="assets/images/staff/patty.png" alt="" />
<h4><div id="tvemployee-6">Patty</div></h4>
<div id="tvemployee-6-bio"><p>Patty has been part of the Fovero family since the beginning. She has helped mold, form, and grow Fovero into what it is today. Patty is a nail technician and when you call to schedule an appointment for a pedicure you can ask for a "Patty-cure" and we\'ll know exactly what you\'re asking for. Patty is so many wonderful things that it is hard to even begin to list them... but here are just a few. She is extremely dedicated, loving, caring and so very passionate about her craft. However, probably one of the best ways to describe her is that she is just a great friend. She truly considers many of her clients as her friends who on a daily basis, she says, enhance her life and we know for a fact that so many of her clients view her as a wonderful friend, also. She is married to wonderful man (who we all know and love) and has 2 kids that we have watched grow up into amazing little people. </p></div>
</li>


<li><img src="assets/images/staff/maria.png" alt="" />
<h4><div id="tvemployee-7">Maria</div></h4>
<div id="tvemployee-7-bio"><p>Maria has been in love with the business of hair her entire life. You could easily say she was influenced by her family\'s own artistic abilities of doing hair. Her main goal is to make others look and feel better about themselves, whether it be with a hair service or just sitting in the chair for a chat. She is always keeping up with the newest fashions and the current trends. Her co-workers call her Mafreaka because she’s got that edgy style. However, she has that amazing ability to add class to that edge of hers.</p></div>
</li>

<li><img src="assets/images/staff/jess.png" alt="" />
<h4><div id="tvemployee-8">Jess</div></h4>
